;The complex eluted as a homogeneous, Gaussian peak, shifted to a smaller elution volume as compared to the protein or RNA alone and the 260 nm absorption was greater than that of the 280 indicating the presence of RNA in that peak.  The structure is highly similar to that of the mouse Dis3L2 (PDB: 4PMW)
